s of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/72557/', '', 'Azelastine, Ketotifen, Lidocaine, Tetracaine, Hydroxocobalamin, Fomepizole, Ipecac, Nitrous acid, Oxygen, Lanthanum carbonate, Deferoxamine, More', '', 1767369485);
